        <section>
            <title>Part (1)</title>
            <body>
                <ol style="lower-alpha">
                    <li><p>Make sure <em style="bold">Coins = 1</em> and <em style="bold">P(heads) =
                                0.5</em>.</p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Press the “<em style="bold">1 Flip</em>” button 3 times.</p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Notice that for each flip, you will see either heads (1) or tails (0)
                            appear in the histogram count. </p>
                    </li>
                  
                </ol>
            </body>
        </section>

        <section>
            <title>Part (2)</title>
            <body>
                <ol style="lower-alpha">
                    <li>
                        <p>Press the <em style="bold">Reset</em> button so that the count is
                            cleared.</p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Make sure <em style="bold">Coins = 1</em> and <em style="bold">P(heads) =
                                0.5</em>. </p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p>This time press the “<em style="bold">10 Flips</em>” button 3 times so
                            that you have 30 coin flips.</p></li>
                </ol>
            </body>
        </section>

        <wb:inline idref="u3_m0_intro5_lbd1_tutor1" purpose="learnbydoing"/>

        <section>
            <title>Part (3)</title>
            <body>
                <ol style="lower-alpha">

                    <li>
                        <p>Press the <em style="bold">Reset</em> button so that the count is
                            cleared. </p></li>
                    <li>
                        <p>Make sure <em style="bold">Coins = 1</em> and <em style="bold">P(heads) =
                                0.5</em>.</p></li>
                    <li><p>Press the <em style="bold">Auto</em> button and watch the count of heads
                            and tails change.</p></li>
                    <li><p>Click the <em style="bold">Pause (II)</em> button once <em style="bold"
                                >Total Flips</em> is over 1,000.</p></li>
                </ol>
            </body>
        </section>
